00:19:50,700 --> 00:19:51,220
If

380
00:19:51,620 --> 00:19:53,180
I become the prince consort,

381
00:19:53,460 --> 00:19:54,490
I will not be able

382
00:19:55,050 --> 00:19:55,980
to be at the frontier
