00:19:56,700 --> 00:19:57,380
I will

384
00:19:57,980 --> 00:19:58,810
be trapped

385
00:19:58,940 --> 00:19:59,530
in the grandeur hall,

386
00:19:59,980 --> 00:20:00,700
