00:20:13,180 --> 00:20:13,660
Your Highness?

391
00:20:16,490 --> 00:20:16,940
Your Highness?

392
00:20:21,530 --> 00:20:22,420
You are right.

393
00:20:23,180 --> 00:20:24,420
Like a pearl hidden under dust.

394
00:20:27,220 --> 00:20:28,700
This shouldn't happen to the one I love.

395
00:20:29,290 --> 00:20:30,860
You should be the sun forever,

