00:31:29,620 --> 00:31:30,570
Hold my hand

576
00:31:33,620 --> 00:31:34,530
and close your eyes.

577
00:31:37,980 --> 00:31:39,140
Imagine what I say

578
00:31:40,290 --> 00:31:41,330
and tell me

579
00:31:42,460 --> 00:31:43,620
what you see.

580
00:31:59,180 --> 00:32:00,220
Imagine

581
00:32:01,730 --> 00:32:03,140
